            <div class="formula-box">
                иқ®иің??пҺҮоһІ = C(49,6) = 13,983,816<br><br>
                йҲӯп—ј?иқҜп„’???= C(6,5) ? C(1,1) = 6 ? 1 = <span class="highlight">6 иқ”?/span><br><br>
                P(йҲӯп—ј?) = 6 / 13,983,816 = 1 / <span class="highlight">2,330,636</span><br><br>
